            "metadata": {
                "abstract": "Motivation: Biobank scale genetic associations results over thousands of traits can be difficult to visualize and navigate. Results: We have created LAVAA, a visualization web-application to generate genetic volcano plots for simultaneously considering the P-value, effect size, case counts, trait class and fine-mapping posterior probability at a singlenucleotide polymorphism (SNP) across a range of traits from a large set of genome-wide association study. We find that user interaction with association results in LAVAA can enrich and enhance the biological interpretation of individual loci. Availability and implementation: LAVAA is available as a stand-alone web service (https://geneviz.aalto.fi/LAVAA/) and will be available in future releases of the finngen.fi website starting with release 10 in late 2023.",
